---
// Mid-page conversion band between Services and Technology.
---

<section class="relative py-16 sm:py-20" aria-label="Get started">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5 sm:px-8">
    <div
      class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-pulse-500/25 bg-void-850 px-7 py-10 text-center sm:px-12"
      data-reveal
    >
      <div
        class="pointer-events-none absolute -top-32 left-1/2 h-64 w-[600px] -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full"
        style="background: radial-gradient(closest-side, rgba(22,194,240,0.14), transparent 70%);"
        aria-hidden="true"
      >
      </div>
      <h2 class="relative font-display text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-mist-100 sm:text-3xl">
        From GPUs to tokens — ready when you are
      </h2>
      <p class="relative mx-auto mt-3 max-w-xl text-mist-400">
        Reserve dedicated capacity or start serving models per-token on the Innoferra platform.
      </p>
      <a
        href="#contact"
        class="relative mt-7 inline-block rounded-full bg-pulse-500 px-7 py-3 font-semibold text-void-950 transition hover:bg-pulse-400"
      >
        Talk to Innoferra
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
